<div class="content-h1">
<h1>《重症》</h1>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="place">
<p id="openCatp" style="display:none">开放分类： <a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" title="文化">文化</a> <a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" title="文学">文学</a> <a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E8%A8%80%E6%83%85%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%B4/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" title="言情小说">言情小说</a></p>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="information" id="unifyprompt">
<div class="summary" id="anchor" name="anchor">
<p>《重症》是作者<a href="//www.baike.com/wiki/%E6%AC%A7%E9%98%B3">欧阳</a>牧师编写的一类如歌行板文学书籍。</p>
<span> <a action="editsummaryhref" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="editSummary();return false;">编辑摘要</a> </span>
</div>
</div>
